#. <section class="sutta" id="sn28.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 28"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 28"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Sāriputtavagga"
msgstr "1. With Sāriputta"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn28.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Upekkhāsutta"
msgstr "4. Equanimity"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn28.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn28.4:1.2"
msgid "Addasā kho āyasmā ānando … pe …"
msgstr "Venerable Ānanda saw Venerable Sāriputta and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn28.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"“vippasannāni kho te, āvuso sāriputta, indriyāni; parisuddho mukhavaṇṇo "
"pariyodāto."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Sāriputta, your faculties are so very clear, and your complexion "
"is pure and bright."

msgctxt "sn28.4:1.4"
msgid "Katamenāyasmā sāriputto ajja vihārena vihāsī”ti?"
msgstr "What meditation were you practicing today?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn28.4:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāhaṃ, āvuso, sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā pubbeva "
"somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ "
"catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend, with the giving up of pleasure and pain, and the ending of former "
"happiness and sadness, I entered and remained in the fourth absorption, "
"without pleasure or pain, with pure equanimity and mindfulness."

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, na evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "But it didn’t occur to me:"

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.3"
msgid ""
"‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’ti "
"vā ‘ahaṃ catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I am entering the fourth absorption’ or ‘I have entered the fourth "
"absorption’ or ‘I am emerging from the fourth absorption’.”"

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.4"
msgid ""
"Tathā hi panāyasmato sāriputtassa dīgharattaṃ ahaṅkāramamaṅkāramānānusayā "
"susamūhatā."
msgstr ""
"“That must be because Venerable Sāriputta has long ago totally uprooted ego, "
"possessiveness, and the underlying tendency to conceit."

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.5"
msgid "Tasmā āyasmato sāriputtassa na evaṃ hoti:"
msgstr "That’s why it didn’t occur to you:"

msgctxt "sn28.4:2.6"
msgid ""
"“‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpajjāmī’ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ samāpanno’"
"ti vā ‘ahaṃ catutthā jhānā vuṭṭhito’ti vā”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I am entering the fourth absorption’ or ‘I have entered the fourth "
"absorption’ or ‘I am emerging from the fourth absorption’.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn28.4:2.7"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
